
<!-- There are special maps available -->
<!-- texture_n  Normal map  -->
<!-- texture_s  Smoothness map, 0 fully rough (matte), 0.5 big specular circle, 0.75 has a small specular circle, 1 is glossy/reflective  -->
<!-- texture_m  Metal map, 0 is non metallic, 1 is metallic.  Metal has colored anodized specular and shine -->
<!-- texture_e  Emissive map, 1 is emissive/fullbright. If you want it to bloom, the underlaying diffuse color needs to be relatively bright -->
<!-- if you do not supply the maps, you can specify a constant value directly using <Metallic>0</<Metallic> or <Smoothness>0</Smoothness> or <Emissive>1</Emissive> etc -->

